Top Dog is a Roguelike style game. The Puppy has been kidnapped by the 
Fat Cat Mafioso. You travel from yard to yard, searching for the 
crafty Cats holding her hostage. Along the way you meet other animals, 
and perhaps a bone or two on the way.

The game is written in Python 2.6, to run:

    python topdog.py


# Known Issues
- holding an inventory item while a NPC gives you a quest item
    will drop the quest item onto the tile you are standing on.
    move off and on again to switch you inventory with the quest item.
- npc's and objects draw together, sometimes a npc draws behind an item
- there is no player death.

url: http://7drl.darknet.co.za/2012/
